rows.label: bf10060100_0010
rows.name: Long time no see, "Father"...

rows.label: bf10060100_0020
rows.name: Logos, huh...

rows.label: bf10060100_0030
rows.name:
So that's my real name?
What does it mean?

rows.label: bf10060100_0040
rows.name:
It has no meaning.
It's just the ego of whoever named you.

rows.label: bf10060100_0050
rows.name:
Hmph...
How many years has it been?

rows.label: bf10060100_0060
rows.name:
I've forgotten.
Time made me forget...

rows.label: bf10060100_0070
rows.name:
You know the reason I came here,
don't you?

rows.label: bf10060100_0080
rows.name:
I know everything.
All that you experience is shared with me here.

rows.label: bf10060100_0090
rows.name: ...Then let's get to the point.

rows.label: bf10060100_0100
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hngh-?!

rows.label: bf10060100_0110
rows.name: Don't rush, my child.

rows.label: bf10060100_0120
rows.name:
I am fading away.
It won't be long now...

rows.label: bf10060100_0130
rows.name: Is that so...?

rows.label: bf10060100_0140
rows.name: I'll take everything.

rows.label: bf10060100_0150
rows.name:
Do as you like.
If you think that's your role...

rows.label: bf10060100_0160
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10060100_0170
rows.name: Is this truly my own choice?

rows.label: bf10060100_0180
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10060100_0190
rows.name:
Answer me.
That's what I came here to find out.

rows.label: bf10060100_0200
rows.name: ...It is the will of all of you.

rows.label: bf10060100_0210
rows.name: ...That's a good answer.

rows.label: bf10060100_0220
rows.name: Thanks for creating me.

rows.label: bf10060100_0230
rows.name: Ah, and here comes the other answer...
